name: Princess Frenchfries
description:
Defend the realm and eat a nice lunch!

[Arrow Keys] or [IJKL] to move

[S] or [Spacebar] to shoot

[D] or [Enter] to burger (activate your powerups)

[P] or [Backspace] to pause

While shooting, you are slower and your shield won't recharge as fast. Your powerups stack up in the BURGER ZONE until you burger them.  There are no lives or game overs, just have fun and get points.

For best results, play in Chrome!
